Head----------Platinum Tiara (ac3 +35HP /+50Mana)&lt;---Frog Crown (12ac 20sv vs fr/cold)<br>
Ears----------Gold Jaspers (x2) (+3Wis)&lt;---Electrum BS (2ac/35hp/25mana), Lose wisdom, but give generally better stats than loops<br>
Face----------Platinum Ruby Veil (+7 Str/Wis)&lt;---Vel Ruby<br>
Neck----------Black Sapphire Play Necklace (+55HP /+55Mana)&lt;---Cherlybol (sp?) Talisman (5ac 3 wis/20mana)<br>
Chest---------Foremens Tunic(AC 10 +3 Str/Wis)&lt;--- Shroud of nauture (13ac 6wis 8sv vs fr/cold)/mith runed (not sure on the stats, never had one myself, all I know is 5wis on it), Both of these tunics will give you the same look you have now, so if you want something different go with gnome skin, no wis, but looks cool<br>
Arms----------Embroidered Black Sleeve (ac4 +10HP /+25Mana)&lt;---Well, Ulthork Hide sleves look kinda cool (8ac 3wis -3dex), but I like ES arms (8ac effect: Drones of Doom), plus you can use them in 3 lvls<br>
Wrists--------Chipped Bone Bracelet(x2) (ac4 +5 Wis)&lt;---Runed Mith Bracers (4ac 3str 5wis), gives a kinda cool purple plate look<br>
Gloves--------Split Paw Gloves (+3 Wis)&lt;---Gnome Skin (some aimless stats, but 2wis) Oh...split paw are 2 wis I believe <br>
Boots---------Golden Efreeti Boots (+9 Int/Wis)<br>
Primary-------Paw of Opolla (ac9 +9agi/wis, +5sta/mana/disease, -5cha)<br>
Secondary----Testament of Vanear (+10 Wis/Mana)&lt;--- Get a Charred Guardian Sheild, lose 10 mana and 1 wis, but gain 10ac<br>
Ranged-------Medicine Totem (ac5 +5 Wis<br>
