</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustraithdarkwood.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Straith Darkwood</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/19/01 11:02:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 42 Druid looking to upgrade and need some advi</span><hr size=1> Curious on the necklas also...I just dont want to spend money if not needed.  I have about 20k in the bank now after selling some things.  I have a chance to get ES Gaunts but I dont know what I should do.  My wis will drop to about 189 if I get the things you say.  I know I will make up for me wis later though. I would really like to have a cool look like I said before.  I have so many questions but dont want to bother you.  I wish I could talk to ya through ICQ or AIM..let me kow..thx <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufyrrwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fyrrwin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/19/01 11:16:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 42 Druid looking to upgrade and need some advi</span><hr size=1> IM Morpheus301 :), am almost always on...am on as we speak :), just packing for a camping trip. Your wis will drop? Huh...maybe I am wrong, but I thought the items I listed bumped it up a bit...didn't do the math, but let's see.<br>
Gloves-Same wis, looks black, nice gloves, stupid verant...halfings can't use :( <br>
Necklace-Gain 3 wis, I personally like it better than the mana/hp one, but I like to focus on a fair amount of ac too. I would only use the mana/hp one when quading...but even then, I still think I would go with my talisman.<br>
Chest-Well...with the gnome you would lose 3wis, but with the runed mith or the Shroud you would gain 2 or 3, but not look as cool.<br>
Face-Would gain 1 wis with the vail<br>
Earings-Lose 6wis, but gain 4ac 50mana and 70hp...now I can equip them and still be at 200 wis, but even if they droped me to 194 I would still wear them, give you mana than +3wis up till around 59 or so...but by then who uses +3iws :)<br>
Sheild-Would lose 1 wis, but gain 10ac...no brainer to me, my book is just rotting in the bank as we speak. <br>
Ok, with not even talking about all of this...let's see what your wis=199 (with the shroud of nature)...I think, let me see if I listed any other items that didn't give wis...didn't see anything. This stuff will probably run ya about 8.5k depending on your server<br>
